item.title: Liz add a quote by Joe Biden
item.description: "Don't tell me what you value, show me your budget, and I'll tell you what you value." -- Joe Biden

item.title: Liz add a quote by Eleanor Roosevelt
item.description: "Life is what you make it. Always has been, always will be." -- Eleanor Roosevelt

item.title: Liz add a quote by Eleanor Roosevelt
item.description: "With the new day comes new strength and new thoughts." -- Eleanor Roosevelt

item.title: Liz add a quote by Eleanor Roosevelt
item.description: "You have to accept whatever comes, and the only important thing is that you meet it with the best you have to give." -- Eleanor Roosevelt

item.title: Liz add a quote by Eleanor Roosevelt
item.description: "In the long run, we shape our lives, and we shape ourselves. The process never ends until we die. And the choices we make are ultimately our own responsibility." -- Eleanor Roosevelt

item.title: Liz add a quote by Eleanor Roosevelt
item.description: "Remember always that you not only have the right to be an individual you have an obligation to be one." -- Eleanor Roosevelt

item.title: Liz add a quote by Eleanor Roosevelt
item.description: "Don't call a woman a bitch. Call her an ass-hole. It still gets your point across and it's not sexist." -- Eleanor Roosevelt

item.title: Liz add a quote by Eleanor Roosevelt
item.description: "I am who I am today because of the choices I made yesterday." -- Eleanor Roosevelt

item.title: Liz add a quote by Charlotte Whitton
item.description: "Whatever women do they must do twice as well as men to be thought half as good. Luckily, this is not difficult." -- Charlotte Whitton

item.title: Liz add a quote by Madonna
item.description: "I'm tough, I'm ambitious, and I know exactly what I want. If that makes me a bitch, okay." -- Madonna

item.title: Liz add a quote by Rebecca West
item.description: "I myself have never been able to find out precisely what feminism is: I only know that people call me a feminist whenever I express sentiments that differentiate me from a doormat." -- Rebecca West

item.title: Liz add a quote by Gloria Steinem
item.description: "A woman without a man is like a fish without a bicycle." -- Gloria Steinem

item.title: Liz add a quote by Cheris Kramarae
item.description: "Feminism is the radical notion that women are human beings." -- Cheris Kramarae

item.title: Liz add a quote by Madeleine Albright
item.description:
"There is a special place in hell for women who don't help other women."
(Keynote speech at <i>Celebrating Inspiration</i> luncheon with the WNBA's All-Decade Team, 2006)" -- Madeleine Albright

item.title: Liz add a quote by Emma Chase
item.description:
"She talks like you. It’s not every day you hear a four-year-old say Prince Charming is a douchebag who’s only holding Cinderella back.”
"That’s my girl." -- Emma Chase

item.title: Liz add a quote by Roseanne Barr
item.description: "The thing women have yet to learn is nobody gives you power. You just take it. " -- Roseanne Barr

item.title: Liz add a quote by Tennessee Williams
item.description: "I've got the guts to die. What I want to know is, have you got the guts to live?" -- Tennessee Williams
